snippet.title: A Day With BTS‚Äôs Jimin in NYC | Vogue
snippet.description:
Vogue spends the day with Jimin of BTS in New York City as he prepares to perform on the Jimmy Fallon Show. Jimin's Fallon appearance comes on the heels of the release of his new song, "Like Crazy," which debuted at No. 1 on the Billboard Hot 100, making Jimin the first South Korean solo artist to reach the top of the charts. 

While perusing a local record shop before rehearing in Times Square, Jimin talks about his anticipated debut solo record, FACE, and gets into what it‚Äôs like performing without his BTS bandmates. 

Jimin‚Äôs new solo album, FACE, is available for streaming here: https://ingrv.es/face

Listen to the main track "Like Crazy" here: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nOI67IDlNMQ
